REACTION   (92-U-235(N,F)ELEM/MASS,CUM,FY,,MXW/REL)
           Yields of cadmium-isotopes relative to 111Cd
COMMENT    The data are the means of measurements in 3 different
            samples, except for 116Cd, where 1 sample was
            contaminated by 116sn.
FLAG       (1.) For mass=113, read =113+114. The sum of the
            measured relative abundances is given, owing to the
            high neutron absorption cross-section of 113Cd.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) Estimated uncertainties include statistical
            uncertainty and uncertainty from correcting for
            natural contamination.
