REACTION   (92-U-235(N,F)ELEM/MASS,CUM,FY,,MXW/REL)
           Yields of tin-isotopes relative to 126Sn
COMMENT    The data are the means of results for 2 samples, on
            each of which measurements at different filament
            temperatures and beam currents were made. The value
            for 124Sn is based on only 1 sample, which was loaded
            with nitric instead of phosphoric acid.
CORRECTION Each measurement was corrected separately for
            contamination, as this factor varied with the
            measurements.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) Uncertainty due to replicated measurements
